	* wait-global.c (_gpgme_wait_global_event_cb): Change type of IDX
	to unsigned int.
	(gpgme_wait): Change type of I and IDX to unsigned int.
	* wait-private.c (_gpgme_wait_on_condition): Change type of IDX
	and I to unsigned int.
