	* gpgme.h (gpgme_get_op_info): Remove prototype.
	* ops.h (_gpgme_set_op_info,
	_gpgme_data_release_and_return_string, _gpgme_data_get_as_string,
	_gpgme_data_append, _gpgme_data_append_string,
