	and move to ...
	* types.h (GpgmeCommandHandler): ... here.
	* engine.h: Don't include "rungpg.h".
	(_gpgme_engine_set_status_handler): Change type of
	argument from GpgStatusHandler to GpgmeStatusHandler.
