	* gpgme.h (GpgmeData_Encoding): New.
	* data.c (gpgme_data_get_encoding,gpgme_data_set_encoding): New.
	* engine-gpgsm.c (map_input_enc): New. Use it in all local
	functions where the INPUT command gets send.

