	* engine-gpgsm.c: Revert last change.

2001-12-14  Marcus Brinkmann  <marcus@g10code.de>

	* engine-gpgsm.c (gpgsm_status_handler): Freeze the output file
	handler when ending this operation, otherwise the wait function
	will sit on it.

